{"lastModified":1761184757768,"uri":"c::8164602117::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nExquisite Luxury\nStep aboard MY Bello, where timeless elegance meets modern sophistication. Designed for an unparalleled sailing experience in captivating waters worldwide, this exceptional yacht offers supreme comfort, world-class service, and endless opportunities for adventure and relaxation.\nEmbark on a journey of pure indulgence.\n\nYear-Round Cruising Adventures\nEmbark on an endless escape as Bello cruises the Mediterranean in summer and ventures to the Caribbean come winter, ensuring year-round adventure wherever she roams.\n\nInviting Deck Spaces & Water Features\nSavor a refreshing dip in the elegantly integrated pool at the beach club, surrounded by plush lounging areas for leisurely sunbathing. Up front, an elevated Jacuzzi promises sweeping views, while another pool on the upper deck sets the stage for sociable relaxation.\n\nElegant Interiors & Seamless Access\nStep aboard and discover a striking glass elevator enfolded by a graceful spiral staircase, ensuring effortless movement between decks. The spacious main saloon with its fold-out balcony welcoming refreshing ocean breezes blends seamlessly into alfresco dining and plush seating, perfect for casual gatherings under the sun.\n\nWellness & Fitness Sanctuary\nImmerse yourself in pure indulgence with a full spa featuring a sauna, massage room, and beauty facilities. An expansive whirlpool with a soothing waterfall, complemented by a lounge and bar, sets the stage for ultimate relaxation. Stay active in the fully equipped gym. Complete with bike, free weights, kettlebells, mats, and ropes, for invigorating on-board workouts.\n\nLuxurious Accommodation with Private Touches\nRetreat to the master suite for sweeping panoramic views and discreet sliding-door access to the foredeck Jacuzzi. The lavish second master cabin offers its own Jacuzzi and private balcony, ideal for savoring ocean vistas complete with a cozy lounge area and separate his-and-hers closets for added exclusivity.\n\nFamily Fun & High-Energy Watersports\nBello’s extensive watersports arsenal: two jet skis, two SeaBobs, two e-foils, and a thrilling waterslide, ensures action-packed adventures for adrenaline seekers. Meanwhile, a dedicated children’s playroom with Pullman beds adds flexibility and fun for the whole family.","blueprint":{"name":"BELLO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2ca1f0-a5c6-11f0-8b47-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2ec4d0-a5c6-11f0-8b4a-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2d1720-a5c6-11f0-8b48-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2aa620-a5c6-11f0-8b47-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2a09e0-a5c6-11f0-8b47-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2f12f0-a5c6-11f0-8b4a-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::f4dadb70-a9d4-11f0-b365-b53439b40659/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2cc900-a5c6-11f0-8b47-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e29e2d0-a5c6-11f0-8b46-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::f4db2990-a9d4-11f0-b365-b53439b40659/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89d3-81819e86f2b8::assets::2e2c53d0-a5c6-11f0-8b47-6fcac25500dc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::587b3280-a5c3-11f0-89